title: Starts of the Week + Week 3 Breakdown, Playing the Odds - Fantasy Football Podcast for 9/22
description:
Week 3 is here! On today’s fantasy football podcast, lots of Week 3 matchup previews and Starts of the Week from Andy, Mike, and Jason! Plus, injury updates, and a new edition of “Never Not Working!” Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for September 22nd, 2022.
